<section id="dir">
  <title>dir</title>
  <para>Directionality - indicates the directionality of content.</para>
  <para><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><emphasis>Type:</emphasis>
    string.<?oxy_custom_end?></para>
  <para><emphasis>Value description:</emphasis>
    <code>"ltr"</code> (Left-To-Right), <code>"rtl"</code> (Right-To-Left), or <code>"auto"</code>
    (determined heuristically, based on the first strong directional character in scope, see <olink
      targetdoc="xliff20.xml" targetptr="uax9">[UAX #9]</olink>).</para>
  <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis> default values for this attribute depend on the element
    in which it is used:</para>
  <itemizedlist>
    <listitem>
      <para>When used in a <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?><olink
          targetdoc="../elements/inline/pc.xml" targetptr="pc"><code>&lt;pc&gt;</code></olink>,
          <?oxy_custom_end?><olink targetdoc="../elements/inline/sc.xml" targetptr="sc"
            ><code>sc</code></olink>, or <olink targetdoc="../elements/inline/ec.xml" targetptr="ec"
            ><code>ec</code></olink>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>object<?oxy_custom_end?>
        that has a <olink targetdoc="../elements/structural/source.xml" targetptr="source"
            ><code>source</code></olink>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>object<?oxy_custom_end?>
        as its parent:</para>
      <para>The value of the <olink targetdoc="srcdir.xml" targetptr="srcdir"
          ><code>srcDir</code></olink>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>string<?oxy_custom_end?>
        of the <olink targetdoc="../elements/structural/unit.xml" targetptr="unit"
          ><code>unit</code></olink>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>object<?oxy_custom_end?>,
        in which the <code>"dir"</code>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>properties<?oxy_custom_end?>
        are located.</para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>When used in a <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?><olink
          targetdoc="../elements/inline/pc.xml" targetptr="pc"><code>&lt;pc&gt;</code></olink>,
          <?oxy_custom_end?><olink targetdoc="../elements/inline/sc.xml" targetptr="sc"
            ><code>sc</code></olink>, or <olink targetdoc="../elements/inline/ec.xml" targetptr="ec"
            ><code>ec</code></olink>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>object<?oxy_custom_end?>
        that has a <olink targetdoc="../elements/structural/target.xml" targetptr="target"
            ><code>target</code></olink>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>object<?oxy_custom_end?>
        as its parent: </para>
      <para>The value of the <olink targetdoc="trgdir.xml" targetptr="trgdir"
          ><code>trgDir</code></olink>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>string<?oxy_custom_end?>
        of the <olink targetdoc="../elements/structural/unit.xml" targetptr="unit"
          ><code>unit</code></olink>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>object<?oxy_custom_end?>,
        in which the <code>"dir"</code>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>properties<?oxy_custom_end?>
        are located.</para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?>When used in a <olink
          targetdoc="../elements/inline/pc.xml" targetptr="pc"><code>&lt;pc></code></olink>,
          <?oxy_custom_end?><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,198,140"?><olink
          targetdoc="../elements/inline/sc.xml" targetptr="sc"><code>&lt;sc></code></olink>, or
          <olink targetdoc="../elements/inline/ec.xml" targetptr="ec"
          ><code>&lt;ec&gt;</code></olink> object that has a
          <?oxy_custom_end?><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?><olink
          targetdoc="../elements/inline/pc.xml" targetptr="pc"><code>&lt;pc></code></olink> element
        as its parent:</para>
      <para>The value of the <olink targetdoc="dir.xml" targetptr="dir"><code>dir</code></olink>
        attribute of the parent <olink targetdoc="../elements/inline/pc.xml" targetptr="pc"
            ><code>&lt;pc&gt;</code></olink> element.<?oxy_custom_end?></para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,198,140"?>When used in <olink
          targetdoc="../elements/structural/data.xml" targetptr="data"
          ><code>&lt;data&gt;</code></olink>:</para>
      <para>The value <code>"auto"</code>.<?oxy_custom_end?></para>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
  <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis>
    <!-- killed on source and target to simplify re-segmentation PRs and to make use of BiDi control characters less likely 
      <olink
  targetdoc="../elements/structural/source.xml"
  targetptr="source"><code>&lt;source&gt;</code></olink>, <olink
  targetdoc="../elements/structural/target.xml"
  targetptr="target"><code>&lt;target&gt;</code></olink>,-->
    <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?><olink
      targetdoc="../elements/structural/data.xml" targetptr="data"
    ><code>&lt;data&gt;</code></olink>, <olink targetdoc="../elements/inline/pc.xml" targetptr="pc"
        ><code>pc</code></olink>,<?oxy_custom_end?>
    <olink targetdoc="../elements/inline/sc.xml" targetptr="sc"><code>sc</code></olink>, and <olink
      targetdoc="../elements/inline/ec.xml" targetptr="ec"><code>ec</code></olink>.</para>
</section>
